_:N30b0455714c64c91990abd581176deaa <http://schema.org/description> "The Architects Registration Board (ARB) regulates the architects’ profession in the UK to ensure that good standards of conduct and practice are consistently maintained. ARB is a public corporation of the Ministry of Housing, Communities and Local Government ." .
